overview: “16 days ago, i was on stage at a sold out Chinateatern, recording this special. Today, you get to see the result. Amazing! To make this happen, I have turned down deals from television networks and invested SEK 500.000 of my own money. I want this to be available to my fans as cheap and as fast as possible. Please don’t pirate this film. I really want this to work and i do want to make more films available this way. Btw, 49kr equals approx. USD 7,3 or EUR 5,5″
title: Magnus Betnér IV
